page.title: 18Schoolgirl in Hinton St G.
page.content: I am tall (1.42 m.) and thin and have long legs, and can run quite fast. I have long brown hair, brown eyes and a brown skin and weigh 35kg. I am 8 years old and my birthday is on Christmas Day. Sometimes I am very shy. Quite often when we go swimming I feel a bit nervous. During playtime at school I like to play horses with my friends or skipping. I like wearing nice clothes and having my hair done. At school I like doing my tables and spelling. When we go home I often have nothing to do, so I get out my spelling and tables straight away and then I don't have to do them later on.
